i'm all set to finish work at the video shop next week! :) so if all goes to plan i only have 2 more shifts to complete; one of which starts in under an hour. woot woot! the other is saturday/tomorrow.
speaking of saturday... this saturday 12th Nov at The Chophouse, The Summer Was Hell are playing. they're awesome. i'll be there with bells on. i don't know if there's a cover charge, but if there is it'll be $10max, but probabaly only $5. oh and in combined celebration of me finishing at the video shop and seeing an awesome band, we plan on heading down the to The Party, getting in for free on our VIP cards, then draining them for all the cheap drinks we can handle. then we'll all troddle back to the chophouse where we'll boogie our little hearts out!
YAY!

see you there!
...don't forget your dancin' shoes!

thats right! i had my first (official) driving lesson this morning! IN A MANUAL! but there's no need to faint like that, i'm not too shabby! i even did a hill start and everything! yeah thats right! well i'm off to work in a sec. but just thought i'd update you all on this mind-blowing event.
i have my next lesson on monday at noon and he said we're gunna do heaps of stuff i.e. highway driving :| I KNOW. oh would you look at the time! best be off!

ashley xo

i was at work tonight and this like grandpa aged guy came in and asked if we had a particular movie and so i typed in the title search of the computer and we didnt have it.
me: "no sorry. we don't"
him: "you dont. oh ok. i'm not from around here, but my son is. so he can just come up here and get anything whenever he wants.
so do u have anything with (some-guy-i'd-never-heard-of) in it?"
me: "we cant actually look up actors names. we can only do title searches."
him: "you dont want to talk to me, fine. i dont want to talk to you. i'll go elsewhere"

he left with the same geniune smile he walked in with, and held onto the whole time he was being insane in my presence.

this is just some random stuff i've seen on trains...

this asian chap was sleeping... then he woke up, removed his shoe, and used it to swat a fly or something against the window, then he went back to sleep.

 

there were these two ladies (one was like 40? and the other was 50?) and they were pretty tipsy...
they attacked this poor gay guy who was 31. not attacked him in a brutal way, just started talking to him (and hitting on him which made it funnier) they were talking to him about his job and their jobs and he was clearly not interested and it was all very humourous! then there was this OTHER guy who had headphones in and his eyes closed. the older lady said to noone in particular
"i think he's an accountant. im going to ask him"  so she did. he was awefully frightened to be awoken(?) by a drunken stranger hovering and swaying over him slurring "are you an accountant?!"
"no?!" was his response....
"haha! oh. well what do you do then?!"
"err... im a project marketer for telstra"
"can i have your card?
"my card?"
"yeah. ur business card!"
"ahh no. im right thanks."
"well can i give you mine?"
"no im right thanks"
"well what do u do as a project manager?"
"i really cant say"
"aww come on!"
"no. i cant. sorry, im done talking" then he put his headphones back in and resumed his upright napping(?) position.
 i laughed. it was extremmely funny. he shut her down. even though he was being a bit too much of an asshole...

 

thats all i got...
have a good one guys!

i feel weird as if i were having an outer-body experience.

first of all i have to apologise for my previous entry...
i was in a bad mood. do you forgive me!? *pouts*

i am now however, excited about the weekend... it's katie's 18th b'day party and it will be a delight!

  • drinky drinky... but not into a coma or anything =P
  • i get to meet all of amy's much-anticipated-to-meet friends (looking forward to that muchly!)
  • get to dress up (not fully over the top or anything, but i like to dress up wherever i go =P)
  • i get to walk through the door arm in arm with my hot date... amy! (omg everyone is sooo jealous already!)
  • and apart from anything else.... IT'S KATIE'S 18TH!!! =D GOOODY!!

i'm also going out this thursday night to that parkwood tavern with alexandria and sammay! i went last thursday with alexandria (and all her friends) and if its anything like last week it should be a blast! i (eventually) got sloshed and ended up finding my old friend and hooking up with him (again) shame. and getting 2 (consensual) smilies... one on each arm. (i really don't think past the moment i'm in at the time!) one's not too bad, it actually looks like a smiley face. the other one however is disgusting! it looks like acid ate away at my skin!! but i was drunk so i couldn't really feel it... now i wear symetrical bandaids to hide my stupidity!

the following thursday i hope to find myself at the party. last time i was there was fanfuckingtastic! i went with sammay and jarrad, and found miranda + (her gf) louise, paton (don't say anything), anika (my best friend from waaaaaaaay back) and some other people i know and don't know. sam and i got shit-faced!! ...only to the point of telling jarrad embarrasing stuff, but not to the point where we couldn't remember doing it =P ....we really have to do that again. although i think we've told jarrad everything... so it might not be as fun for you this time! =P lol 

so anyway, thats all in my world at the moment! :) i'll keep you posted as more news unfolds! moohahaha!
